      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation on at least three systematically refined meshes with GCI below 5% for hemolysis index QoI.",
      "rationale": "Three-mesh Richardson extrapolation performed; GCI for hemolysis index is 8.3%, exceeding the 5% threshold; achieved level capped at 3."
