      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions fully replicate VAD operating envelope including hematocrit range, temperature, and inlet waveform.",
      "rationale": "Bench tests performed at fixed 40% hematocrit and steady inflow only; pulsatile VAD waveform and physiological temperature variation not replicated; two-gradation gap."
