      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (e.g., E_rel) with uncertainty bounds demonstrating agreement within 15% for absolute hemolysis index.",
      "rationale": "Relative error is 22% with overlapping uncertainty intervals; systematic over-prediction observed at high RPM; two-gradation shortfall."
